---
title: Roasted Duck Leg with Garlicky Cavolo Nero and Red Wine Sauce
description: We love a good Duck Leg  with Cavolo Nero and Sauce and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
